{
  "chapter": 14,
  "chapter_summary": "第十四回：梦中的女人\n\n夕阳下的湖畔，小马与太阳神的使者展开对峙。使者以神秘魅力诱惑小马皈依太阳神教，但小马坚决拒绝，挥拳相向。然而使者轻功绝顶，轻松避开小马的攻击。\n\n使者揭示湖上花舟中有一女神，正是小马魂牵梦萦的小琳。小琳已被太阳神教控制，神情恍惚，对小马视若无睹。小马心碎欲绝，跃入湖中追逐花舟却无法接近。\n\n小马沉入冰冷湖水后被救起，发现老皮已被太阳神教控制，精神失常。使者最后给出两条路：皈依或死亡。小马想起好友丁喜的教诲\"死并不能解决问题\"，最终选择活下去。\n\n本章揭示了太阳神教的控制手段，展现了小马与小琳的情感纠葛，以及小马在绝境中的心理转变。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "text": "你就是太阳神的使者？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我知道，我正在等着你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你若是诚心贩依，我就收容你，引导你到极乐和永生。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "text": "死就是永生？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "有时是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "text": "那么你为什么不去死？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你打空了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "text": "这一次打空了，还有第二次。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你还想再试试？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "text": "只要你的鼻子还在脸上，我的拳头还在手上，我们就永远没完！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "等一等！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "text": "等什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "等我先让你看一个人。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "text": "看谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "当然是个很好看的人，我保证你一定很想着她。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你看过了她之后，如果还想打碎我鼻子，我绝不还手！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "text": "这个人究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "严格说来，现在她已经不能算是人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "text": "不是人是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "是女神。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "text": "她在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "就在那里！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你看我怎么样？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "可是我自己觉得好极了，简直从来都没有这么好过！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "到了这里后，我才知道以前的日子都是白活的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "滚。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你叫我滚我就滚。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "现在你还有两条路可走。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shen_de_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "如果你真心皈依我，现在还来得及；如果你想死，也方便得很。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "死，并不是解决问题的法子，只有懦夫才会用死来解脱。只要你活着，只要你有决心、有勇气，无论多艰苦困难的事，都一定有法子解决的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不想死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    }
  ],
